  "title": "RefinementList/Menu: allow to provide manual values",
  "body": "One thing people struggle a lot with is being able to create a RefinementList or a Menu using manual values instead of the API ones.\n\nWe need to be able to easily answer the \"I want to create a menu with those 5 colors in it, I have 10 colors in my index\".\n\nThere might be other widgets where this makes sense, have a look.\n",
